title: Littleton #1 Two Bedroom ~ Best Price! ~ Ready September! Downtown
posting_body: ['Welcome Home!', 'Call or TEXT to schedule your showing today!', 'Spacious Cozy Comfortable 2 bed apartment ready for move in September 22!', 'Situated on a beautiful Lake, within view of the Rocky Mountains, this property is the perfect escape from the city.', 'Features stainless appliances, large closets and ample storage.', 'Community amenities include calming courtyards, fire pits, pool, fitness center and indoor spa.', 'Thoughtful use of space?', 'Check.', 'Modern design elements?', 'Check.', "This property has everything you've come to expect from a luxury home- and much more.", 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Hardwood-Look Flooring', 'Wood-burning Fireplaces with Marble Hearths', 'Vaulted Ceilings', 'Custom Cabinetry and Lighting Package', 'Two-Tone Paint', 'Full Size Washers/Dryers', 'Generous Linen and Pantry Storage', 'Exterior Storage', 'Spacious Closets', "You will love your new home but you can't spend all your time indoors.", "At this property you won't want to.", 'The community spaces are designed to both relax and entertain.', 'Clubhouse with FREE WiFi and Computer Access', 'Covered Parking', 'Cardio Fitness Center', 'Swimming Pool with Spacious Sun Deck', 'Indoor Heated Spa', 'Social Areas with Barbecue Grills', 'Beautiful Duck Ponds', 'Stunning Mountain and Lake Views', 'Lush, Mature Landscaping', 'Call or TEXT to schedule your showing today!', '*Restrictions Apply, pricing, availability, and lease terms subject to change anytime.']
